        <item>
            <title>日本環球影城「咚奇剛國度」12 月 11 日開幕，過山車、主題餐廳、精品店搶先睇</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/11/12/donkey-kong-country/hottopic/walk/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=donkey-kong-country</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/11/12/donkey-kong-country/hottopic/walk/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Pickle Rick]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Tue, 12 Nov 2024 11:00:14 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[旅遊]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[玩樂好去處]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Super Nintendo World]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[任天堂]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[咚奇剛國度]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1274367</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p style="font-weight: 400;">任天堂董事宮本茂宣佈，日本大阪環球影城「Super Nintendo World」（Super Nintendo World）將在今年 12 月 11 日推出全新擴展園區「咚奇剛國度」（Donkey Kong Country）。園區內設有機動遊戲、主題餐廳及精品店。</p><div class="epyt-video-wrapper"><iframe  style="display: block; margin: 0px auto;"  id="_ytid_90814"  width="590" height="332"  data-origwidth="590" data-origheight="332" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/HUbSpOcunTg?enablejsapi=1&#038;autoplay=0&#038;cc_load_policy=0&#038;cc_lang_pref=&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;loop=0&#038;modestbranding=1&#038;rel=0&#038;fs=1&#038;playsinline=1&#038;autohide=1&#038;theme=light&#038;color=white&#038;controls=1&#038;" class="__youtube_prefs__  epyt-is-override  no-lazyload" title="YouTube player"  allow="fullscreen; accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen data-no-lazy="1" data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll=""></iframe></div><p style="text-align: center;">▲「咚奇剛國度」（Donkey Kong Country）將在今年 12 月 11 日開幕（圖片來源：<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=HUbSpOcunTg">任天堂</a>）</p><p style="font-weight: 400;">「咚奇剛國度」以熟悉的《咚奇剛》遊戲元素為主題，貫穿叢林與黃金神廟等經典場景。遊客可以透過新增的咚奇剛與狄狄剛專屬互動手環，配合手機應用程式參與到多種沉浸式體驗當中，而舊款手環也適用於新園區。在園區內，不只可以探索隱藏在各處的互動裝置，還能收集遊戲印章，體驗包括音樂節奏遊戲「康加鼓節奏擊鼓」等特色活動，讓遊客仿如親身參與到咚奇剛的動作世界中。</p><p><img fetchpriority="high" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1274371 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/screenshot20241111at-5-694x376.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="376" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/screenshot20241111at-5-694x376.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/screenshot20241111at-5-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1274378 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/screenshot20241111at-10-694x374.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="374" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/screenshot20241111at-10-694x374.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/screenshot20241111at-10-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1274372 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/screenshot20241111at-6-694x373.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="373" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/screenshot20241111at-6-694x373.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/screenshot20241111at-6-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲貫穿叢林與黃金神廟（圖片來源：<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=HUbSpOcunTg">任天堂</a>）</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1274375 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/screenshot20241111at-8-694x372.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="372" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/screenshot20241111at-8-694x372.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/screenshot20241111at-8-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲遊客可以透過新增的咚奇剛與狄狄剛專屬互動手環（圖片來源：<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=HUbSpOcunTg">任天堂</a>）</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1274376 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/screenshot20241111at-9-694x386.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="386" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/screenshot20241111at-9-694x386.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/screenshot20241111at-9-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲配合手機應用程式參與到多種沉浸式體驗當中（圖片來源：<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=HUbSpOcunTg">任天堂</a>）</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1274374 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/screenshot20241111at-7-694x374.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="374" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/screenshot20241111at-7-694x374.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/screenshot20241111at-7-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲音樂節奏遊戲「康加鼓節奏擊鼓」（圖片來源：<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=HUbSpOcunTg">任天堂</a>）</p><p style="font-weight: 400;">「咚奇剛國度」設有「咚奇剛的瘋狂礦車」，是一款以礦車為主題的過山車遊樂設施，遊客可隨著礦車飛馳穿越叢林，體驗不可預測的驚險轉折。過山車的身高要求為 122 釐米以上（有監護人陪同時可放寬至 107 釐米），而整段遊玩時間約為兩分鐘。過山車的面貌並未在宣傳片中完全揭露，留待遊客親身探索。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1274380 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/screenshot20241111at-11-694x386.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="386" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/screenshot20241111at-11-694x386.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/screenshot20241111at-11-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1274381 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/screenshot20241111at-12-694x385.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="385" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/screenshot20241111at-12-694x385.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/screenshot20241111at-12-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲「咚奇剛的瘋狂礦車」的面貌並未在宣傳片中完全揭露，留待遊客親身探索（圖片來源：<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=HUbSpOcunTg">任天堂</a>）</p><p style="font-weight: 400;">除了刺激的遊樂設施，「咚奇剛國度」亦設有專屬餐飲與購物選擇，例如餐廳「Jungle Beat Shake」提供以香蕉為主題的特製飲品和甜品。園區內還開設了「Funky Kong&#8217;s Fly and Buy」精品店，供應一系列咚奇剛及狄狄剛周邊商品。遊客還有機會與咚奇剛本人會面及合照。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1274382 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/screenshot20241111at-13-694x386.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="386" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/screenshot20241111at-13-694x386.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/screenshot20241111at-13-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1274383 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/screenshot20241111at-14-694x389.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="389" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/screenshot20241111at-14-694x389.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/screenshot20241111at-14-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1274384 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/screenshot20241111at-15-694x389.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="389" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/screenshot20241111at-15-694x389.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/screenshot20241111at-15-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲餐廳「Jungle Beat Shake」提供以香蕉為主題的特製飲品和甜品（圖片來源：<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=HUbSpOcunTg">任天堂</a>）</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1274387 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/screenshot20241111at-17-694x389.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="389" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/screenshot20241111at-17-694x389.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/screenshot20241111at-17-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1274388 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/screenshot20241111at-18-694x388.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="388" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/screenshot20241111at-18-694x388.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/screenshot20241111at-18-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲「Funky Kong&#8217;s Fly and Buy」精品店供應一系列咚奇剛及狄狄剛周邊商品（圖片來源：<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=HUbSpOcunTg">任天堂</a>）</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1274386 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/screenshot20241111at-16-694x388.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="388" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/screenshot20241111at-16-694x388.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/screenshot20241111at-16-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲遊客還有機會與咚奇剛本人會面及合照（圖片來源：<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=HUbSpOcunTg">任天堂</a>）</p><p>資料及圖片來源：<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=HUbSpOcunTg">任天堂</a></p><br /><b>
]]>
            </description>
